This directory contains a source snapshot of nut.js (Apache-2.0) for local
secondary development.

Upstream: https://github.com/nut-tree/nut.js
License: Apache License 2.0

Native prebuilt bindings used at runtime come from the public npm package
`@nut-tree-fork/nut-js` (and its platform packages), not from building this
tree in-place. Modify sources here when forking behavior; wire runtime
imports in packages/desktop-control/src accordingly.

Workspace isolation:
- Nested `package.json` files were renamed to `package.upstream.json` so pnpm
  workspace globs (`packages/**`) do not treat vendored packages as workspace
  members (those manifests referenced paid/unavailable `@nut-tree/*` natives).
